# Workflow Test Matrix

| Workflow | Purpose | Command | Type |
|---|---|---|---|
| App/module syntax | Catch immediate syntax failures | `[SYNTAX_COMMAND]` | static/smoke |
| App startup import | Ensure app factory/module loads | `[SMOKE_COMMAND]` | smoke |
| Auth/security posture | Ensure auth and security route posture remains enforced | `[TARGETED_TEST_COMMAND]` | workflow-targeted |
| Full local verify | Standard pre-handoff gate | `[VERIFY_COMMAND]` | gate |
| Full suite coverage | Detect regressions and enforce minimum confidence | `[COVERAGE_COMMAND]` | regression |

## Policy
- Every behavior change must map to at least one targeted test command.
- New workflow = add matrix row in the same change.
- Smoke scenarios are cataloged in `docs/SMOKE_TEST_CATALOG.md`.
